<div class="jumbotron">
	<h1 class="display-4">AWS Video Transcriber</h1>
	<p class="lead">The AWS Video Transcriber provides a simple, serverless framework to generate and edit closed captions for all of your video content.</p>
	<hr class="my-4">
	<p>It uses <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/s3/">Amazon S3</a> to store video content, <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/lambda/">AWS Lambda</a> to trigger processing, <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/mediaconvert/">Amazon MediaConvert</a> to extract audio files and <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/transcribe/">Amazon Transcribe</a> to create closed captions.</p>
	<p>Simply deploy the solution to your account, upload videos to the nominated S3 bucket, fine tune your closed captions and download your completed WEBVTT/SRT captions.</p>

	<div id="loginLogout"></div>
</div>

